{"tid":429000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿中央政府貪腐　巴西南部三州獨立公投","createTime":"2017-10-08T13:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T18:18:28.000Z","uid":60545,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"77a9b80720dc1de621a69e72c0dc86b73dc4acd6","tid":429000,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"為了抗議中央政府貪腐，巴西最南部的三個州，周六（7日）舉行無約束力的獨立公投。<br />\n<br />\n巴拉那州（Parana）、南里奧格蘭德州（又譯南大河州，Rio Grande do Sul）及聖卡塔琳娜州（Santa Catarina），周六舉行獨立公投。由於巴西憲法明文禁止分離主義，主辦單位坦承，三個州的獨立公投沒有拘束力，投票可能不會很熱烈，但西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區的獨立公投，已立下國際先例。<br />\n<br />\n三州的總人口估計約有2千9百萬人口，主辦單位期望能有100萬人參與投票，來凸顯民眾期望脫離巴西利亞政府（Brasilia，巴西首都）的貪腐統治。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171008/1218731/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171008%2F1218731%2F&d=L%2Bf6m%2BCTEttU5uIL0P8PbEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e2503b7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171008/1218731/</a>"},{"pid":"665e7c4d4f1d8545d27b512c60a73c014197a259","tid":429000,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f0c19930fd677b39353216e9cc16453ab1bdde","tid":429000,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oct8近期活躍五毛<br />\nJR<br />\n三色貓<br />\n民國復興<br />\n蘇麗珊<br />\n國語好手<br />\nbb chu<br />\nRedbaron<br />\nnewlife<br />\n優美開始<br />\n阿古路<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"03adf9cc1984d7e243b63cc333e2cb975d0a9302","tid":429000,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d82de43374d65541983ee62a790d44112c62855","tid":429000,"uid":18245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT